{
  "stem": "10496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's just like-- the only education I got was basically real life experiences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And learning to play chess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- oh, and chess.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, I-- I had a sort of a rough beginning, because they put me in a-- I think the fifth grade, you know, where I should have been much higher.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got some double promotions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But still, I-- I graduated high school at age 20.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it didn't make any difference, because when I went to college I had a lot of students that were my age, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm always considered--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the German refugee over in-- in-- in Winthrop, Massachusetts, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they accepted me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jewish population accepted me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the-- and I became very active, very quickly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I had some problems with the-- like the McLaughlin gang, you know, that they--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were a whole bunch of 12 to 13 cousins, and I guess they-- they didn't want any stranger, or they-- they thought I was a Nazi or something, you know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- they gave me a hard time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I once remember I had to run for my life from those kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were kind of-- they were pretty rough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they threw rocks at us and all that business-- at me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had already made some friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were in the same-- they had the same problem that I had because they were supporting me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right-- at that point, it was anti-German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think anti-- I was a-- I was-- you know, they were not-- probably not smart enough to realize that I was-- I was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here, too.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well,I knew it was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a temporary situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
